Title: Veet Hair Removal Cream Brightening Normal to Dry - (Pack of 3)
Description: If you want to get rid of stubborn hair gently yet effectively, this Brightening Veet hair removal cream, for normal to dry skin, is what you should be using. Enriched with microbeads Besides keeping your skin moisturized your skin for up to 24 hours, these microbeads also remove dead skin cells, so your skin looks brighter. Removes short, stubborn hair This hair removal cream works close to the skin, to uproot even the most stubborn hair from the roots. How To Use: Evenly spread the cream on your skin, coating the hairs completely, using the curved part of the spatula. After 3 minutes, use the spatula to gently remove a small area of the cream to see if the hair comes off easily. If it does, remove the rest of the cream. If your hair is stubborn, you can leave the cream on for up to 6 minutes in total, not longer than that. Thoroughly rinse your skin with water to wash away the hair completely, and then pat dry. Precautions: Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. The application time should NOT exceed 6 minutes. This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples.  Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to hair removal creams in the past.  Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. Before every use, test your skin’s reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.

Title: Veet Full Body Waxing Kit Normal (Pack of 3)
Description: Waxing does not always have to be painful and messy. In fact, you can do it yourself in the comfort of your home. It’s all thanks to this pack full body waxing kit from Veet. For normal skin Containing Shea Butter and Berries that are known for their moisturizing properties, this waxing kit gives your skin the kind of moisturizing that it needs. Easy Grip Tabs The Easy Grip tab of each waxing strip allows you to get a firm hold of them so you can effectively uproot hair as short as 1.5mm, and so your skin stays smooth and exfoliated for up to 4 weeks. With regular use, you’ll notice your hair becoming softer, finer, and fewer. How To Use: Step 1 - Rub the wax strip between your hands so it’s easy to separate. Step 2 - Test the product on your legs before moving on to sensitive areas like your underarms and bikini line, if it’s your first experience with waxing. For use on the underarm, cut the strips into suitable sizes and make the area taunt by lifting your elbow up. Place the strips in different directions, keeping in mind the opposite directions in which hair on the upper and lower part of the underarm grow. For use on the bikini line, cut the strips into suitable sizes and be sure to only use on small areas at a time. For best results: Thoroughly wash your skin with soap and water before waxing. Pull back the wax strip against the direction of hair growth, to completely uproot them. The wax strips can be reused until they lose their stickiness. Precautions: Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples. Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to waxing in the past. Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. Hair should be between 2mm and 5mm long for you to have a comfortable waxing session. You can trim the hair with scissors before waxing if it’s longer. If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. Before every use, test your skin’s reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.
